ist)|Oksana Grishina]]|RUS|2000 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Iryna Yanovych]]|UKR|2000 Summer}}\n|-\n| time trial<br>{{DetailsLink|Cycling at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's track time trial}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[F\u00e9licia Ballanger]]|FRA|2000 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Michelle Ferris]]|AUS|2000 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Jiang Cuihua]]|CHN|2000 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Mountain biking==\n{| {{MedalistTable|type=Event}}\n|-\n| Men's <br>{{DetailsLink|Cycling at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's cross-country}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Miguel Martinez (cyclist)|Miguel Martinez]]|FRA|2000 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Filip Meirhaeghe]]|BEL|2000 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Christoph Sauser]]|SUI|2000 Summer}}\n|-\n| Women's <br>{{DetailsLink|Cycling at the 2000 Summer Olympics \u2013 Women's cross-country}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Paola Pezzo]]|ITA|2000 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Barbara Blatter]]|SUI|2000 Summer}}\n|{{flagIOCmedalist|[[Margarita Fullana]]|ESP|2000 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==Medal table==\n{{Medals table\n | caption        = \n | host           = \n | flag_template  = FlagIOCteam\n | event          = 2000 Summer\n | team           = \n | gold_FRA = 5 | silver_FRA = 2 | bronze_FRA = 1\n | gold_GER = 3 | silver_GER = 4 | bronze_GER = 3\n | gold_NED = 3 | silver_NED = 1 | bronze_NED = 0\n | gold_ITA = 2 | silver_ITA = 0 | bronze_ITA = 1\n | gold_AUS = 1 | silver_AUS = 2 | bronze_AUS = 3\n | gold_GBR = 1 | silver_GBR = 1 | bronze_GBR = 2\n | gold_RUS = 1 | silver_RUS = 1 | bronze_RUS = 2\n | gold_USA = 1 | silver_USA = 1 | bronze_USA = 0\n | gold_ESP = 1 | silver_ESP = 0 | bronze_ESP = 1\n | gold_BEL = 0 | silver_BEL = 2 | bronze_BEL = 0\n | gold_SUI = 0 | silver_SUI = 1 | bronze_SUI = 1\n | gold_UKR = 0 | silver_UKR = 1 | bronze_UKR = 1\n | gold_KAZ = 0 | silver_KAZ = 1 | bronze_KAZ = 0\n | gold_URU = 0 | silver_URU = 1 | bronze_URU = 0\n | gold_CHN = 0 | silver_CHN = 0 | bronze_CHN = 1\n | gold_LTU = 0 | silver_LTU = 0 | bronze_LTU = 1\n}